Debug stub: restore registers of suspended threads

This change simply fills in natp-&gt;suspended_registers structure for
service_runtime.

Added debug stub test that uses ctrl+c to _suspend_ the thread, then uses single
step to check it works (for x86 that means flags register was successfully
changed).

